column2: Activate Maven extensions during project resolution.

column3:
Load extensions so custom transports can be registered, and invoke
AbstractMavenLifecycleParticipant#afterSessionStart() and #afterProjectsRead()
so extensions have a chance to modify the project model.

Fixes IDEA-119940 Maven extensions not activated
http://youtrack.jetbrains.com/issue/IDEA-119940
